reviewText:
This DVD contains 4 episodes from the Peg & Cat cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. The Tree Problem
2. Another Tree Problem
3. Yet Another Tree Problem
4. The Baby Problem
My one year old can not go a day without Peg and cat. This video must play before we pull off.anf have saved me from.many headaches
Whole family loves Peg & Cat. Some of the best episodes here.
Some of the best children's programing on tv is through PBS and I am grateful that I can purchase such quality entertainment for my child
My son loves this series! Great buy :)
Bought this for my 15 mo grand daughter. She loves it! Highly recomend.
My son has this on repeat in the xbox. We had to buy more already.
